name: MYRE
description: Myre is the name of the newly born puppy of Myro and Ada, the beloved dogs of Raj Gokal and Anatoly Yakovenko, the co-founders of Solana. Inspired by Grok, Myre emerges as the newly born princess of Solana and the heir to the Iron Throne of the Solana blockchain & is followed by Toly on X.
